<div class="main-body">
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="page-header">
      <div class="page-header-title">
        <h4>관리</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="page-header-breadcrumb">
        <ul class="breadcrumb-title">
          <li class="breadcrumb-item">
            <a href="/">
              <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#!">메일발송</a></li>
          <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#!">관리</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page-body">
      <div class="row" id="listTable">
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <div class="alert alert-default" style="border-radius:  0; border-width:  2px;  margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          	<ul class="p-l-15 f-12" style="list-style-type: disc; color:  #666;">
              	<li>대량발송은 보내기 버튼을 클릭 후 시간 소요 될 수 있으므로 보내기 버튼을 여러 번 클릭하거나 새로 고침 하는 경우 메일이 중복발송이 되거나 메일이 발송 중 중단이 될 수 있으므로 주의하시기 바랍니다.</li>
                <li>메일 수정 시, 예약 설정된 메일은 예약이 취소되므로 주의하시기 바랍니다.</li>
          	</ul>
        	</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
              <select name="select" class="col-md-1 form-control form-control-default m-b-10 p-r-5 f-left" id="selectKeyword">
                <option>키워드</option>
                <%for(var i=0; i < klist.length; i++) {%>
                  <option value='<%=klist[i].keyword_idx%>'><%=klist[i].keyword_main%></option>
                <%}%>
              </select>
              <div class="col-sm-3 p-l-5 p-t-5 m-b-10 f-left border-checkbox-section">
                <div class="border-checkbox-group border-checkbox-group-default m-r-5">
                  <input class="border-checkbox" type="checkbox" id="searchBtn1" name="search" value="1">
                  <label class="border-checkbox-label" for="searchBtn1">인비테이션</label>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-3 f-right col-sm-9 m-l-10 p-l-0 p-r-0  m-b-10 right-icon-control">
                <input type="text" class="p-t-10 form-control form-control-default search-text" id="keywordInput">
                <div class="form-icon" id="searchBtn">
                  <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
              <select id="selectSearchType" name="select" class="col-12 col-md-1 form-control form-control-default f-right search-select">
                <option value="t">제목</option>
                <option value="n">발송차수</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="card-block table-border-style">
              <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table">
                  <thead>
                    <tr>
                      <th width="1%">NO</th>
                      <th width="5%">키워드</th>
                      <th width="15%">제목</th>
                      <th width="5%">발송자</th>
                      <th width="5%">발송차수</th>
                      <th width="5%">수신자</th>
                      <th width="20%">수신그룹</th>
                      <th width="5%">작성일</th>
                      <th width="5%">예약일</th>
                      <th width="5%">발송일</th>
                      <th width="25%">관리</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    <%
                      var limit = 20;
                      if(currentPage > 0){
                        (currentPage - 1) * limit;
                      }
                      for(var i=0; i < list.length; i++) {
                        var recipiArr = list[i].M_recipi_idx.split(',');
                        var recipiStr = '';
                        if(recipiArr.length > 1){
                          recipiStr = ((list[i].M_recipi == null)? '(삭제된메일)':list[i].M_recipi)+' 외 '+(recipiArr.length-1);
                        }
                        else{
                          recipiStr = ((list[i].M_recipi == null)? '(삭제된메일)':list[i].M_recipi);
                        }

                        var groupStr = '';
                        if(list[i].M_group_idx != null){
                          var groupArr = list[i].M_group_idx.split(',');
                          if(groupArr.length > 1){
                            groupStr = ((list[i].M_group == null)? '(삭제된그룹)':list[i].M_group)+' 외 '+(groupArr.length-1);
                          }
                          else{
                            groupStr = ((list[i].M_group == null)? '(삭제된그룹)':list[i].M_group);
                          }
                        }
                    %>
                    <tr>
                      <th><%= listCount - i - offset %></th>
                      <td><div class="kwd_nobr"><%= list[i].keyword %></div></td>
                      <td>
                        <a href="http://showbox.email/preview?keyword=<%= list[i].M_keyword_idx %>&idx=<%= list[i].n_idx %>" target="_blank">
                          <div class="title_nobr"><%= list[i].M_subject %></div>
                        </a>
                      </td>
                      <td><%= list[i].M_sender %></td>
                      <td><div class="num_nobr"><%= ((list[i].M_invitation == '0')?(list[i].M_seq_number+'차'):'-') %></div></td>
                      <td><%= recipiStr %></td>
                      <td><div class="group-nobr" title="<%= groupStr %>"><%= groupStr %></div></td>
                      <td><div class="date-nobr"><%= list[i].M_regdate %></div></td>
                      <td><div class="date-nobr"><%= (list[i].M_type != 1) ?'-': list[i].M_send %></div></td>
                      <td><div class="date-nobr"><%= ((list[i].M_send == null) || (list[i].M_type == 1 &&list[i].success ==0 &&list[i].fail==0)) ?'-': list[i].M_send %></div></td>
                      <td>
                        <%if(list[i].M_send == null  || (list[i].M_type == 1 &&list[i].success ==0 &&list[i].fail==0)){%>
                          <button class="btn btn-sm btn-inverse btn-send" data-idx="<%= list[i].n_idx %>">보내기</button>
                        <%}else{%>
                          <button class="btn btn-sm btn-inverse btn-resend" data-idx="<%= list[i].n_idx %>">재발송</button>
                        <%}%>
                        <button class="btn btn-sm btn-inverse btn-delete" data-idx="<%= list[i].n_idx %>">삭제</button>
                        <%if(list[i].M_send == null || (list[i].M_type == 1 &&list[i].success ==0 &&list[i].fail==0)){%>
                          <button class="btn btn-sm btn-inverse btn-edit" data-idx="<%= list[i].n_idx %>">수정</button>
                        <%}%>
                        <button class="btn btn-sm btn-inverse btn-rewrite" data-idx="<%= list[i].n_idx %>">재작성</button>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <% } %>
                  </tbody>
                  <tfoot>
                    <%
                    var pageCount = Math.ceil(listCount/limit);
                    if(pageCount > 1) {
                    %>
                    <tr>
                      <td colspan="11">
                        <ul class="pagination float-right">
                          <%
                            var pageSize = 5;
                            var pRCnt = parseInt(currentPage / pageSize);
                            if(currentPage % pageSize == 0){
                              pRCnt = parseInt(currentPage / pageSize) - 1;
                            }
                            if(currentPage > 5) {
                          %>
                            <li class="page-item">
                              <a class="page-link" data-value="1" aria-label="Previous">
                                <i class="ti-angle-double-left f-12"></i>
                                <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                              </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="page-item">
                              <a class="page-link" data-value=="<%=(pRCnt * pageSize)%>" aria-label="Previous">
                                <i class="ti-angle-left f-12"></i>
                                <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                              </a>
                            </li>
                          <% } %>
                          <% for(var index=pRCnt * pageSize + 1;index<(pRCnt + 1)*pageSize + 1;index++){%>
                            <li class= "<%=(currentPage == index) ? 'active' : ''%> page-item">
                              <a class="page-link" data-value="<%=index%>" >
                                <%= index %>
                              </a>
                            </li>
                          <%
                              if(index == pageCount) {
                                break;
                              }
                            }
                          %>
                          <% if((pRCnt + 1) * pageSize < pageCount) { %>
                            <li class="page-item">
                              <a class="page-link" data-value="<%=(pRCnt + 1)*pageSize+1%>" aria-label="Next">
                                <i class="ti-angle-right f-12"></i>
                                <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                              </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="page-item">
                              <a class="page-link" data-value="<%=pageCount%>" aria-label="Next">
                                <i class="ti-angle-double-right f-12"></i>
                                <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                              </a>
                            </li>
                          <% } %>
                        </ul>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <% } %>
                  </tfoot>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <input type="hidden" id="page" value="<%=page%>"/>
      <input type="hidden" id="ivt" value="<%=ivt%>"/>
      <input type="hidden" id="keyword" value="<%=keyword%>"/>
      <!-- Modal start-->
      <div class='modal fade' id='previewMail-Modal' role='dialog'>
        <div class='modal-dialog modal-lg' role='document'>
          <div class='modal-content'>
            <div class='modal-header'>
              <h5 class="modal-title"><span id="date"></span>미리보기</h5>
              <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                <span aria-hidden="true">×</span>
              </button>
            </div>
            <div class='modal-body'>
              <div class='col-sm-12' id="mailBody"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button class="btn btn-secondary mobtn" data-dismiss='modal' aria-label='Close' type="button">취소</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Modal end-->
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
